text:
Website Design Note
This website was created using RStudio and Quarto. The “cosmo” theme provides a clean and professional appearance suitable for academic content. The navigation bar includes links to the homepage, about page, and assignments for easy navigation. A resume page is also added for quick access to professional information. The site is structured to reflect both academic and professional aspects of the author’s work.
